extends ../generate/layout/_layout

block title
  - var title = "Privacy policy"

block content
    main.main
        +banner.banner--wide

        section.section
            .container-fluid
                .container
                    .title
                        h1.title__text= title
                    .info-section
                        strong Last updated: 26.02.2026
                        br
                        br
                        p Heaffen (“we”, “our”, “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our website and services (the “Platform”).
                        p By using Heaffen, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
                        br
                        h2 1. Information We Collect
                        p We may collect the following types of information:
                        br
                        h3 1.1 Information You Provide Directly
                        p When you:
                        ul
                            li Submit a candidate profile
                            li Post a job listing
                            li Fill out a contact form
                            li Upload a CV
                            li Contact us via email
                        p We may collect:
                        ul
                            li Full name
                            li Email address
                            li Phone number / Telegram / LinkedIn
                            li Location
                            li Professional information
                            li Salary expectations
                            li Work preferences
                            li Resume files (PDF)
                            li Company information (for employers)
                        br
                        h3 1.2 Automatically Collected Information
                        p When you use the platform, we may automatically collect:
                        ul
                            li IP address
                            li Browser type
                            li Device type
                            li Operating system
                            li Pages visited
                            li Time spent on pages
                            li Referring URLs
                        p This information helps us improve the platform and user experience.
                        br
                        h2 2. How We Use Your Information
                        p We use collected information to:
                        ul
                            li Publish candidate profiles and job listings
                            li Connect candidates and employers
                            li Improve platform functionality
                            li Respond to inquiries
                            li Send important service updates
                            li Prevent fraud and abuse
                            li Comply with legal obligations
                            li We do not sell personal data to third parties.
                        br
                        h2 3. Public Information
                        p If you submit a candidate profile or job listing, certain information may be publicly displayed on the platform, including:
                        ul
                            li Professional title
                            li Experience level
                            li Skills
                            li Salary expectations
                            li Company details (for employers)
                        p Sensitive contact details may be hidden depending on platform settings.
                        br
                        h2 4. Data Sharing
                        p We may share your data only:
                        ul
                            li With employers (for candidate profiles)
                            li With candidates (for job listings)
                            li With service providers who help operate the platform (hosting, analytics, payment processing)
                            li If required by law
                            li All third-party providers are required to protect your data.
                        br
                        h2 5. Data Storage & Security
                        p We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against:
                        ul
                            li Unauthorized access
                            li Alteration
                            li Disclosure
                            li Destruction
                        p However, no online system can guarantee absolute security.
                        br
                        h2 6. Data Retention
                        p We retain your personal data:
                        ul
                            li For as long as your profile or listing is active
                            li As necessary to comply with legal obligations
                            li Until you request deletion
                        p You may request deletion of your data at any time.
                        br
                        h2 8. Cookies
                        p We may use cookies and similar technologies to:
                        ul
                            li Improve user experience
                            li Analyze traffic
                            li Remember user preferences
                        p You can manage cookies through your browser settings.
                        br
                        h2 9. Third-Party Links
                        p The platform may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., LinkedIn, company websites). We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
                        br
                        h2 10. Children’s Privacy
                        p Heaffen is not intended for individuals under 18 years old. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.
                        br
                        h2 11. Changes to This Policy
                        p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
                        p Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
                        br
                        h2 12. Contact Us
                        p For questions regarding these Terms, please contact:
                        br
                        p
                            | Email:
                            a(href="#") [Insert Email]
                        p
                            | Website:
                            a(href="#") [Insert Website URL]
